## Limitations

This report is based on data and articles available up to October 2023. The situation is dynamic, and ongoing developments in the political, economic, and social landscapes may further influence the ammunition market. Additionally, the report relies on publicly available information, which may not capture all aspects of the industry, such as proprietary data from manufacturers.